    <note>Zhang(1) Rui [10008] Author of Ji feng bei ji fang, 1 ch., Ji feng pu ji fang, 30 ch. Both prefaces dated 1133 according to Ding Fubao, 479a-480a. Notice of the bei ji fang in SS, YWZ, 6.26b (ch 6, p. 122). He was active during the Zhenghe period and moved to Sichuan (Shu) in Shaoxing (1131-1162). He became famous through his treatment of Murong(1) Yanfeng's mother [10451]. The Guest call number of the pu ji fang is C103/2458. Selections in YLDD, 1037.1a- (Vol. 10-11). CBD, 3,  2317.</note>
